d-ed3cff6bf876.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcnv6ne1zqyro%232%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20mother%20of%20Ann%20Grosmaire%2C%2019%2C%20who%20was%20shot%20dead%20by%20her%20boyfriend%2C%20explains%20why%20she%20chose%20restorative%20justice.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcnv6ne1zqyro%3Fat_medium%3DRSS%26at_campaign%3Drss%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22FCC%20chair%20threatens%20to%20pull%20licenses%20of%20broadcasters%20airing%20'distortions'%20about%20the%20Iran%20war%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224350%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22FCC%20Chair%20Brendan%20Carr%20sits%20at%20a%20desk%20with%20a%20serious%20expression.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b5f958a96e437d6eb8549e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBrendan%20Carr%20threatened%20to%20revoke%20the%20broadcast%20licenses%20of%20news%20outlets%20for%20their%20coverage%20of%20the%20Iran%20war.%3Cp%3EAl%20Drago%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EFCC%20Chair%20Brendan%20Carr%20threatened%20broadcasters'%20licenses%20over%20their%20coverage%20of%20the%20Iran%20war.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20didn't%20target%20specific%20networks%2C%20but%20said%20any%20broadcaster%20publishing%20%26quot%3Bdistortions%26quot%3B%20is%20at%20risk.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHis%20threat%20came%20after%20a%20Trump%20post%20criticizing%20The%20New%20York%20Times%20and%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffcc-brendan-carr-laura-ingraham-stephen-colbert-equal-time-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EFederal%20Communications%20Commission%3C%2Fa%3E%20Chair%20Brendan%20Carr%20warned%20broadcasters%20Saturday%20that%20they%20could%20lose%20their%20licenses%20if%20they%20air%20what%20he%20described%20as%20misleading%20coverage%20of%20the%20war%20involving%20Iran.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20Carr%20said%20broadcasters%20spreading%20inaccurate%20reporting%20should%20%26quot%3Bcorrect%20course%26quot%3B%20before%20coming%20license%20renewals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBroadcasters%20that%20are%20running%20hoaxes%20and%20news%20distortions%20%E2%80%94%20also%20known%20as%20the%20fake%20news%20%E2%80%94%20have%20a%20chance%20now%20to%20correct%20course%20before%20their%20license%20renewals%20come%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20Carr%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BThe%20law%20is%20clear.%20Broadcasters%20must%20operate%20in%20the%20public%20interest%2C%20and%20they%20will%20lose%20their%20licenses%20if%20they%20do%20not.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20did%20not%20specify%20which%20broadcasters%20may%20be%20at%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECarr's%20comments%20included%20a%20screenshot%20of%20a%20Truth%20Social%20post%20from%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20accusing%20major%20newspapers%20of%20misrepresenting%20developments%20in%20the%20war%2C%20which%20began%20with%20US%20and%20Israeli%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-says-us-launched-strikes-iran-kharg-island-oil-reserves-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estrikes%20on%20Iranian%20targets%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20has%20since%20escalated%20across%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20wrote%20that%20headlines%20reporting%20that%20Iranian%20strikes%20had%20destroyed%20tanker%20aircraft%20at%20a%20Saudi%20base%20were%20%26quot%3Bintentionally%20misleading%2C%26quot%3B%20saying%20the%20planes%20were%20not%20destroyed%20and%20that%20most%20were%20already%20back%20in%20service.%20Trump%20singled%20out%20The%20New%20York%20Times%20and%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%2C%20writing%20that%20their%20coverage%20was%20%26quot%3Bthe%20exact%20opposite%20of%20the%20actual%20facts.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FCC%20regulates%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcomcast-fcc-brendan-carr-trump-dei-investigation-paramount-disney-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebroadcast%20television%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20radio%20stations%20and%20grants%20them%20licenses%20to%20use%20public%20airwaves%2C%20which%20must%20be%20renewed%20periodically.%20The%20warning%20reflects%20a%20broader%20pattern%20of%20the%20FCC%20under%20Carr%20taking%20a%20more%20aggressive%20posture%20toward%20broadcasters'%20content%2C%20and%20comes%20amid%20heightened%20tensions%20between%20broadcasters%20and%20the%20FCC%20over%20how%20political%20content%20is%20handled%20on%20air.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20becoming%20chair%20during%20Trump's%20second%20term%2C%20Carr%20has%20repeatedly%20pointed%20to%20the%20agency's%20%26quot%3Bpublic%20interest%26quot%3B%20standard%20and%20a%20rarely%20invoked%20%26quot%3Bnews%20distortion%26quot%3B%20policy%20as%20potential%20tools%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-fcc-brendan-carr-broadcast-licenses-cbs-nbc-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Escrutinize%20stations'%20programming%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20CBS%20opted%20not%20to%20air%20a%20scheduled%20interview%20with%20Texas%20state%20Rep.%20James%20Talarico%20on%20%26quot%3BThe%20Late%20Show%20with%20Stephen%20Colbert%26quot%3B%20after%20network%20lawyers%20warned%20the%20appearance%20could%20trigger%20the%20FCC's%20%26quot%3Bequal%20time%26quot%3B%20rule%2C%20which%20requires%20stations%20to%20provide%20comparable%20airtime%20to%20political%20candidates.%20The%20commission%20has%20recently%20signaled%20that%20late-night%20talk%20shows%20may%20not%20qualify%20for%20a%20long-assumed%20exemption%20to%20the%20rule%20and%20has%20also%20pursued%20enforcement%20actions%20related%20to%20a%20similar%20interview%20on%20ABC's%20%26quot%3BThe%20View.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECritics%2C%20including%20former%20FCC%20officials%20and%20lawmakers%2C%20have%20warned%20that%20using%20those%20authorities%20to%20challenge%20editorial%20decisions%20risks%20pressuring%20news%20organizations%20over%20their%20coverage%2C%20while%20Carr%20has%20defended%20the%20approach%20as%20ensuring%20broadcasters%20meet%20their%20legal%20obligations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECarr's%20warning%20contrasts%20with%20comments%20he%20made%20earlier%20in%20his%20career.%20In%20a%202019%20post%20on%20X%2C%20the%20then-commissioner%20wrote%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20FCC%20does%20not%20have%20a%20roving%20mandate%20to%20police%20speech%20in%20the%20name%20of%20the%20'public%20interest%2C'%26quot%3B%20a%20statement%20critics%20have%20resurfaced%20as%20he%20increasingly%20invokes%20that%20standard%20to%20scrutinize%20broadcasters'%20programming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffcc-chair-brendan-carr-threatens-broadcast-licenses-over-iran-coverage-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773535709000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b5fc3fa96e437d6eb854b0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffcc-chair-brendan-carr-threatens-broadcast-licenses-over-iran-coverage-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Carr's%20threat%2C%20targeting%20unspecified%20broadcasters%2C%20amplified%20Donald%20Trump's%20criticism%20of%20coverage%20by%20The%20New%20York%20Times%20and%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ktl%40businessinsider.com%20(Katherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffcc-chair-brendan-carr-threatens-broadcast-licenses-over-iran-coverage-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20women%20bringing%20chess%20into%20the%2021st%20Century%20-%20with%20'bullet'%20matches%20and%20viral%20videos%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773535218000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci