s%20on%20Saturday%20amid%20the%20ongoing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Firan-gambles-drones-missiles-can-outlast-us-and-israel-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emilitary%20conflict%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20Middle%20East.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlumes%20of%20dark%20black%20smoke%20billowed%20around%20the%20Port%20of%20Fujairah%2C%20the%20only%20multipurpose%20maritime%20facility%20on%20the%20UAE's%20east%20coast.%20The%20Fujairah%20government's%20media%20office%20said%20debris%20from%20an%20intercepted%20drone%20caused%20the%20fire.%20No%20injuries%20were%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fire%20comes%20after%20Iran%20said%20it%20would%20retaliate%20against%20the%20US%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-says-us-launched-strikes-iran-kharg-island-oil-reserves-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eattacking%20Kharg%20Island%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Friday.%20Kharg%20Island%2C%20located%20about%20300%20miles%20from%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz%2C%20is%20key%20to%20Iran's%20oil%20industry%20and%20has%20refineries%20that%20process%20nearly%20all%20of%20the%20country's%20oil%20exports.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%20said%20the%20US%20had%20%26quot%3Btotally%20obliterated%26quot%3B%20military%20targets%20on%20Kharg%20Island%20in%20a%20Truth%20Social%20post%20on%20Friday.%20In%20a%20Truth%20Social%20post%20on%20Sunday%2C%20Trump%20said%20he%20hoped%20other%20countries%20affected%20by%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz%20closure%20would%20send%20warships%20alongside%20the%20US%20to%20help%20secure%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWar%20broke%20out%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20last%20month%20when%20the%20US%20and%20Israel%20launched%20joint%20strikes%20against%20Iran.%20In%20response%2C%20Iran%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Firan-missiles-multiple-countries-what-happened-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etargeted%20US%20military%20bases%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20neighboring%20countries%20like%20Qatar%2C%20Bahrain%2C%20Kuwait%2C%20and%20the%20UAE.%20The%20ongoing%20military%20conflict%20has%20shuttered%20airspaces%20and%20halted%20most%20traffic%20through%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz.%20US%20strikes%20on%20Kharg%20Island%20and%20damage%20to%20the%20UAE's%20Port%20of%20Fujairah%20could%20impact%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foil-price-100-iran-war-tanker-attacks-hormuz-reserve-release-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoil%20prices%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20again%20surged%20past%20%24100%20on%20Friday%2C%20driving%20up%20gas%20prices%20around%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESmoke%20from%20the%20coast%20of%20Fujairah%20spread%20over%20the%20Gulf%20of%20Oman.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222455%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22NASA%20MODIS%20satellite%20image%20of%20Fujairah%20on%20March%2014%2C%202026.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b592c9a7a4f9df67ba5a3f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221498%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENASA%20MODIS%20satellite%20image%20of%20Fujairah%20on%20March%2014%2C%202026.%3Cp%3ENASA%20Modis%20satellite%20image%2C%20November%2014%2C%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20satellite%20image%20taken%20on%20Saturday%20showed%20smoke%20from%20the%20fire%20spreading%20over%20the%20Gulf%20of%20Oman.%20The%20Port%20of%20Fujairah%20exported%20an%20average%20of%201.7%20million%20barrels%20of%20crude%20oil%20and%20refined%20fuels%20each%20day%20in%202025%2C%20Reuters%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESome%20operations%20at%20the%20Port%20of%20Fujairah%20were%20suspended%20on%20Saturday.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222666%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Fujairah%20in%20the%20UAE%20on%20March%2014%2C%202026.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b59437a96e437d6eb8542c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAP%20Photo%2FAltaf%20Qadri%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigc