20will%20lead%20to%20autonomy%20and%20abundance%20for%20humans.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Uber-famous%20founder%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fformer-uber-ceo-travis-kalanick-said-he-moved-to-texas-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETravis%20Kalanick%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20says%20a%20new%20golden%20age%20is%20coming%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it's%20robots%20that%20are%20ushering%20it%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKalanick%20announced%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftravis-kalanick-ex-uber-misfits-entering-robotics-game-atoms-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Enew%20venture%20called%20Atoms%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Friday%20in%20a%201%2C600-word%20screed%20in%20which%20he%20said%20the%20automation%20of%20the%20physical%20world%20is%20the%20next%20phase%20of%20the%20AI%20era.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSoftware%20has%20automated%20tasks%20of%20language%20and%20math%2C%20but%20the%20complete%20automation%20of%20the%20physical%20world%20%E2%80%94%20autonomy%20%E2%80%94%20remains%20largely%20untouched%20territory%2C%20the%20principal%20unlock%20to%20the%20next%20era%20of%20progress%20and%20abundance%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BHistory%20refers%20to%20this%20kind%20of%20moment%20of%20radical%20progress%20as%20a%20Golden%20Age.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKalanick%20said%20this%20%26quot%3Bgolden%20age%26quot%3B%20is%20emerging%20as%20production%20and%20transportation%20become%20driven%20primarily%20by%20computation%2C%20minerals%2C%20and%20energy.%20With%20autonomous%20machines%20building%20other%20machines%20and%20software%20constantly%20improving%20itself%2C%20he%20said%2C%20productivity%20could%20reach%20unprecedented%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20organization%20of%20human%20capital%20becomes%20superhuman%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKalanick%20later%20said%20on%20the%20tech%20talk%20show%20TBPN%20on%20Friday%20that%20Atoms%20has%20been%20operating%20in%20stealth%20mode%20for%20the%20past%20eight%20years.%20Now%2C%20the%20company%20aims%20to%20expand%20its%20delivery%20infrastructure%20beyond%20food%20into%20industries%20such%20as%20food%20service%2C%20mining%2C%20and%20transportation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20in%20his%20announcement%20that%20the%20company's%20goal%20is%20to%20create%20%26quot%3Bgainfully%20employed%20robots.%26quot%3B%20He%20defines%20these%20as%20%26quot%3Bspecialized%20robots%20with%20productive%20jobs%20that%20bring%20abundance%20to%20their%20owners%20and%20society%20at%20large.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20humans%20should%20be%20careful%20about%20building%20robots%20in%20their%20own%20image.%20%26quot%3BI%20watched%20the%20half-marathon%20and%20couldn't%20help%20but%20think%20how%20much%20better%20it%20would%20be%20if%20they%20just%20had%20wheels%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%2C%20referring%20to%20a%20competition%20in%20Beijing%20last%20year%20that%20pitted%20humanoid%20robots%20against%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKalanick%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsenior-director-engineering-uber-shares-promotion-journey-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecofounded%20Uber%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202009.%20He%20led%20the%20company%20as%20CEO%20until%202017%2C%20when%20he%20stepped%20down%20amid%20reports%20of%20a%20toxic%20workplace%20culture%20and%20ongoing%20regulatory%20battles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20isn't%20the%20only%20tech%20executive%20who%20believes%20AI%20robots%20should%20extend%20beyond%20humanoid%20form.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cofounder%20and%20CEO%20of%20World%20Labs%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffei-fei-li-world-labs-ai-childhood-immigrant-dry-cleaner-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EFei-Fei%20Li%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20on%20the%20No%20Priors%20podcast%20last%20year%20that%20building%20physical%20AI%20in%20a%20singular%20form%20is%20energy%20inefficient.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20an%20extreme%20and%20trivial%20example%2C%20if%20we%20put%20robots%20underwater%2C%20they%20should%20not%20be%20the%20shape%20of%20humans%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20better%20be%20in%20the%20shape%20of%20fish.%20Just%20think%20about%20energy%20efficiency.%20The%20same%20with%20flying.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftravis-kalanick-atoms-uber-humanoid-robots-golden-age-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773514921000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b5a240a7a4f9df67ba5a5b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftravis-kalanick-atoms-uber-humanoid-robots-golden-age-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Travis%20Kalanick%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Uber%20and%20its%20former%20CEO%2C%20unveiled%20his%20new%20robotics%20company%2C%20Atmos%2C%20on%20Friday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lvaranasi%40businessinsider.com%20(Lakshmi%20Varanasi)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftravis-kalanick-atoms-uber-humanoid-robots-golden-age-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Phil%20Campbell%2C%20Mot%C3%B6rhead%20Guitarist%2C%20Dead%20at%2064%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773513954000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236688004%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Phil%20Campbell%2C%20the%20guitarist%20for%20the%20rock%20band%20Mot%C3%B6rhead%2C%20died%20on%20Friday%20following%20a%20battle%20in%20intensive%20care%20after%20a%20major%20operation.%20He%20was%2064.%C2%A0%20His%20death%20was%20confirmed%20in%20a%20statement%20posted%20to%20the%20Phil%20Campbell%20and%20the%20Bastard%20Sons%20Instagram%20account.%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20with%20great%20sadness%20that%20we%20announce%20the%20passing%20of%20our%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Payton%20Turkeltaub%22%2C%22e