3EQueens%2C%20New%20York%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20often%20ask%20me%20why%20my%20Mom%20and%20Pop's%20arts-and-crafts%20studio%20in%20New%20York%20is%20called%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2F2ndchancecandles.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2nd%20Chance%20Candles%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20answer%20is%20simple%3A%20your%20past%20doesn't%20define%20your%20future%2C%20and%20everyone%20deserves%20a%20second%20chance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20living%20this%20truth%20after%20overcoming%20an%20addiction%20that%20nearly%20killed%20me.%20I%20am%20now%20sober%2C%20running%20a%20business%20that%20brings%20me%20joy%20and%20fulfillment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ac9a9448-f2d9-459a-ba57-8834125ee2ff%5C%22%3EI%20got%20kicked%20out%20of%20the%20college%20dorms%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20always%20been%20a%20great%20kid%20growing%20up%20in%20Putnam%20County%2C%20New%20York.%20I%20had%20a%20high%20GPA%20and%20planned%20to%20start%20a%20career%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F4-signs-youre-not-brushing-your-teeth-correctly-2021-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edental%20hygiene%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20alcohol%20and%20weed%20in%20which%20I%20dabbled%20during%20my%20senior%20year%20of%20high%20school%20took%20hold%20in%20college.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20dry%20campus%2C%20and%20I%20got%20kicked%20out%20of%20the%20dorms%20after%20being%20caught%20drinking%20with%20friends.%20I%20didn't%20have%20a%20car%2C%20so%20I%20couldn't%20commute.%20At%2019%2C%20I%20had%20to%20move%20back%20in%20with%20my%20parents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20outside%20a%20candle-making%20store.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a9f47cd3e2f1aef36a14ca%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDevine%20outside%20her%20studio.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Lisa%20Devine%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBack%20at%20home%2C%20I%20couldn't%20follow%20the%20rules.%20It%20was%20a%20small%20town%2C%20and%20I%20left%20for%20New%20York%20City.%20Real%20fast%2C%20I%20got%20my%20first%20job%20working%20in%20a%20caf%C3%A9.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20come%20home%20after%20work%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freference%2Fmarijuana-effects%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esmoke%20pot%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Then%2C%20in%202011%2C%20someone%20offered%20me%20heroin.%20I%20knew%20I%20was%20in%20trouble%20when%20my%20dealer%20didn't%20pick%20up%20one%20day%2C%20and%20I%20started%20to%20throw%20up%20from%20withdrawal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHave%20you%20overcome%20a%20significant%20challenge%20in%20life%3F%20Please%20email%20Jane%20Ridley%20at%20jridley%40insider.com%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20you're%20a%20functioning%20addict%2C%20your%20new%20normal%20is%20under%20the%20influence.%20If%20I%20didn't%20have%20drugs%2C%20I%20didn't%20feel%20normal.%20Still%2C%20I%20kept%20getting%20high%20while%20holding%20down%20my%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22af3b20db-d620-424a-a7bd-521b2b936f20%5C%22%3EI%20went%20through%20a%205-day%20detox%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202016%2C%20I%20was%20arrested%20on%20charges%20relating%20to%20drugs.%20I%20had%20no%20criminal%20record%20at%20that%20point%2C%20and%20I%20was%20clearly%20an%20addict.%20The%20court%20mandated%20that%20I%20either%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdifference-between-jail-and-prison%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ego%20to%20prison%20%3C%2Fa%3Eor%20enter%20treatment%20for%20a%20year.%20I%20chose%20rehab.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20already%20gone%20through%20a%20five-day%20detox.%20It%20was%20awful%20and%20took%20me%20about%20six%20months%20to%20start%20feeling%20OK.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20end%2C%20I%20remained%20in%20sober%20living%20for%2019%20months.%20Next%20I%20studied%20at%20a%20trade%20school%20for%20dentistry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20worked%20as%20a%20barista%20during%20that%20time%2C%20which%20was%20a%20great%20opportunity%20to%20get%20back%20on%20my%20feet.%20It%20was%20exactly%20what%20I%20wanted%20and%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThings%20went%20well%20for%20five%20years.%20Then%2C%20in%202021%2C%20I%20stopped%20caring%20for%20myself%20and%20relapsed.%20This%20time%2C%20my%20drug%20of%20choice%20was%20cocaine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'll%20never%20forget%20those%20incredibly%20miserable%20days.%20I%20hit%20rock%20bottom%20and%20found%20the%20strength%20to%20check%20myself%20into%20rehab.%20I%20worked%20hard%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fformer-chef-restaurateur-founded-snack-brand-split-overcame-addiction-2020-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eon%20my%20recovery%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20my%20new%20clean%20date%20is%20April%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20my%20partner%20had%20read%20up%20about%20the%20candle-making%20business.%20He%20suggested%20it%20might%20be%20a%20good%20way%20to%20make%20money%3B%20a%20means%20for%20me%20to%20become%20the%20upstanding%20person%20in%20society%20I%20longed%20to%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b2a04f54-4e4b-4d0e-94a8-635bb7a0e0ff%5C%22%3EI%20host%20groups%20like%20the%20Girl%20Scouts%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20making%20hand-poured%20candles%20at%20home%20and%20opened%20a%20brick-and-mortar%20store%20in%20October%202023.%20I%20felt%20immensely%20proud%20of%20how%20far%20I'd%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20made%20perfect%20sense%20to%20call%20it%20%26quot%3B2nd%20Chance%20Candles.%26quot%3B%20I%20loved%20telling%20customers%20about%20the%20name%20because%20it's%20inspiring.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20sold%20my%20scented%20candles%20in%20jars.%20The%20real%20joy%20came%20from%20doing%20workshops%20for%20groups%20like%20the%20Girl%20Scouts.%20I%20got%20such%20a%20kick%20out%20of%20the%20sessions%20because%20I%20got%20to%20share%20my%20craft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20with%20rows%20of%20bottles%20in%20front%20of%20her.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a9f565fd4fbd083f299dc2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDevine%20with%20the%20scent%20bottles%20clients%20use%20during%20their%20candle-making.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Lisa%20Devine%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20an%20open%20book%2C%20and%20though%20I%20don't%20particularly%20like%20talking%20about%20my%20past%2C%20it's%20a%20good%20conversation%20starter.%20A%20lot%20of%20people%20in%20the%20community%20know%20my%20recovery%20story%20and%20give%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20vowed%20never%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcelebrities-struggle-with-addiction-recovery-relapse-2018-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ereturn%20to%20my%20addiction%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20I'll%20always%20remember%20the%20horrible%20fog%20of%20my%2020s%20and%20early%2030s.%20It's%20terrifying%20to%20think%20I%20could%20have%20died%20from%20an%20overdose.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20work%2C%20I've%20hosted%20many%20fun%20events%2C%20including%20kids'%20birthday%20parties%20and%20corporate%20workshops.%20We've%20branched%20out%20into%20slime-making%20and%20drop%20painting%20with%20acrylics%2C%20and%20I%20employ%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fearn-extra-money-with-these-21-high-paying-side-jobs-2019-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epart-time%20staff%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20help%20in%20the%20studio.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I%20could%20give%20my%20younger%20self%20advice%2C%20it%20would%20be%20this%3A%20You%20are%20not%20your%20worst%20mistake.%20Shame%20keeps%20you%20stuck%20longer%20than%20addiction%20does.%20Ask%20for%20help%20sooner%2C%20and%20know%20that%20rebuilding%20and%20success%20are%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20