%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20wasn't%20sure%20if%20my%20daughter%20was%20ready%20to%20sleep%20over%20at%20a%20friend's%20on%20her%20own.%20I%20decided%20to%20join%20her.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222481%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mom%20and%20daughter%20at%20sleepover%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a72d91fd4fbd083f297135%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221861%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20joined%20her%20daughter%20at%20a%20sleepover.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMy%20daughter%20was%20invited%20to%20sleep%20over%20at%20her%20close%20friend's%20house.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHer%20friend's%20mom%20and%20I%20talked%2C%20and%20we%20agreed%20that%20I%20would%20sleep%20over%2C%20too.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20was%20a%20huge%20success%2C%20and%20later%20her%20friend%20and%20mom%20slept%20over%20at%20our%20place.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20excited%20when%20my%20daughter%20Aria%20was%20invited%20to%20spend%20the%20night%20at%20a%20friend's%20house.%20While%20I%20realize%20not%20everyone%20experiences%20this%20rite%20of%20passage%20or%20even%20needs%20to%2C%20I%20view%20it%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparent-milestones-are-equally-important-as-baby-milestones-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Enice%20milestone%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwearable-sleeping-bag-2016-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECozy%20sleeping%20bags%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20tasty%20snacks%2C%20movie%20marathons%2C%20and%20laughing%20with%20friends%20way%20past%20bedtime%20can%20make%20for%20fun%2C%20fond%20memories.%20I%20was%20not%20allowed%20to%20sleep%20over%20anywhere%20until%20middle%20school%2C%20and%20even%20then%2C%20it%20was%20a%20tough%20sell%20to%20my%20mom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20my%20enthusiasm%2C%20I%20still%20had%20some%20trepidation%20about%20letting%20Aria%20sleep%20over.%20I%20had%20known%20her%20friend's%20parents%20for%20a%20while%2C%20and%20I%20trusted%20them%20fully%2C%20so%20that%20part%20wasn't%20an%20issue.%20Rather%2C%20I%20was%20unsure%20how%20Aria%20would%20do%20on%20her%20own%3A%20would%20she%20get%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthings-that-scared-people-as-kids-2018-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Escared%20in%20the%20dark%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20she%20sometimes%20does%20at%20home%3F%20Would%20the%20sleeping%20arrangements%20be%20comfortable%3F%20Would%20she%20be%20warm%20enough%3F%20Too%20warm%2C%20perhaps%3F%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20and%20other%20concerns%20swirled%20around%20in%20my%20head.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222ec3ac4b-fdd2-4a03-8891-543945660449%5C%22%3EI%20want%20to%20foster%20her%20independence%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdrop-off-birthday-party-restaurant-parenting-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EFostering%20independence%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20important%20to%20me%20as%20a%20parent%2C%20but%20it%20is%20also%20important%20that%20Aria%20feels%20OK.%20The%20other%20mom%20and%20I%20talked%3B%20she%20understood%20and%20had%20even%20more%20concerns%20for%20her%20child%20sleeping%20at%20someone%20else's%20house%20than%20I%20did.%20So%2C%20we%20decided%20that%20I%20would%20come%20too.%20I%20knew%20I%20risked%20being%20called%20a%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-hosts-play-club-where-kids-are-free-helicopter-parents-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehelicopter%20parent%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20my%20goal%20was%20to%20help%2C%20not%20hover.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221877%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Girl%20with%20rollie%20suitcase%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a734511fb3fcb42648d750%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223724%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author's%20daughter%20packed%20her%20bag%20for%20her%20sleepover%20with%20her%20friend%20and%20both%20moms.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20talked%20to%20my%20daughter%20and%20asked%20if%20she%20felt%20OK%20about%20me%20tagging%20along.%20To%20my%20relief%2C%20Aria%20was%20happy%20about%20this%20joint%20opportunity%20for%20mommy%20to%20come%20and%20put%20a%20new%20spin%20on%20the%20term%20%26quot%3Bgirls'%20night%26quot%3B.%20She%20packed%20her%20fox-covered%20suitcase%20with%20clothes%2C%20her%20toothbrush%2C%20jammies%2C%20and%20way%20more%20toys%20than%20needed%3B%20I%20packed%20mine%20(minus%20the%20toys).%20When%20Aria%20and%20I%20arrived%2C%20she%20and%20her%20friend%20were%20thrilled%20to%20see%20each%20other%20and%20set%20off%20toward%20the%20bedroom%20to%20play.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20mom%20and%20I%20enjoyed%20chatting%20while%20the%20girls%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freference%2Fhow-to-make-slime%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estretched%20slime%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20built%20bendable%20cities%2C%20and%20played%20pretend.%20We%20let%20them%20stay%20up%20a%20little%20later%20than%20usual%2C%20but%20nothing%20extreme.%20They%20brushed%20their%20teeth%20side%20by%20side%20in%20the%20mirror%20and%20got%20ready%20to%20lie%20down.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20girls%20were%20asleep%2C%20the%20mom%20and%20I%20each%20enjoyed%20a%20glass%20of%20wine%20and%20more%20adult%20conversation%20before%20she%20retired%20to%20her%20room%2C%20and%20I%20slept%20on%20the%20couch.%20All%20in%20all%2C%20the%20night%20went%20off%20without%20a%20hitch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224f5258f1-c565-4f87-bfcf-dcd5b78cb1a4%5C%22%3EThen%20we%20switched%20houses%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMonths%20later%2C%20we%20did%20the%20same%20thing%20at%20my%20house.%20I%20hosted%20a%20sleepover%20in%20honor%20of%20the%3Cem%3E%20%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3ELord%20of%20the%20Rings%3A%20The%20Fellowship%20of%20the%20Ring%26quot%3B%20anniversary%20(the%20girls%20know%20nothing%20of%20Frodo%20or%20Mordor%2C%20but%20the%20mom%20and%20I%20are%20big%20fans).%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20welcomed%20them%20in%20my%20Arwen%20costume%2C%20and%20the%20girls%20went%20off%20to%20play.%20This%20time%2C%20we%20had%20a%20third%20adult%20present%2C%20who%20doesn't%20have%20children%20but%20loves%20our%20girls%20(and%20LOTR).%20The%20three%20adults%20watched%20some%20of%20the%20trilogy%2C%20had%20some%20wine%2C%20dinner%2C%20and%20conversation.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20night%2C%20Aria's%20friend%20tried%20to%20sleep%20in%20Aria's%20trundle%20bed%20but%20soon%20grew%20scared%2C%20so%20she%20went%20to%20sleep%20with%20her%20mom%20instead%2C%20who%20was%20right%20there%20and%20ready%20to%20ease%20those%20nighttime%20fears.%20The%20following%20morning%2C%20I%20made%20waffles%20for%20everyone%20before%20we%20said%20goodbye%20and%20reflected%20on%20how%20much%20fun%20the%20night%20had%20been.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222b73eda3-66d6-4751-a19b-851949341e68%5C%22%3ETagging%20along%20for%20sleepovers%20can%20be%20fun%20for%20everyone%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20these%20parent-child%20sleepovers%20could%20be%20a%20fresh%20idea%20for%20caregivers%20and%20a%20nice%20middle%20ground%20between%20spending%20the%20night%20and%20just%20having%20a%20playdate.%20I%20view%20what%20we%20did%20as%20a%20compromise%20where%20the%20child%20still%20gets%20to%20have%20an%20overnight%20experience%2C%20but%20someone%20is%20there%20in%20case%20anything%20arises.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdmittedly%2C%20this%20might%20not%20work%20for%20everyone.%20The%20mother%20and%20I%20know%20each%20other%20well%20enough%20to%20do%20this.%20I%20also%20had%20the%20good%20fortune%20of%20my%20daughter%20being%20OK%20with%20my%20attendance%2C%20so%20there%20was%20no%20sour%20mood%20to%20spoil%20the%20evening.%20And%20I%20have%20a%20kid%20of%20elementary%20age%20%E2%80%94%20I'm%20not%20sure%20if%20this%20would%20work%20with%20a%20kid%20in%20high%20school.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20people%20m