rial%20steps%20forward%20toward%20emergence%2C%26quot%3B%20Spirit's%20president%20and%20CEO%2C%20Dave%20Davis%2C%20said%20in%20a%20press%20release.%20%26quot%3BI%20also%20want%20to%20thank%20our%20team%20members%20and%20guests%20for%20their%20support%20as%20we%20work%20together%20to%20build%20a%20stronger%20Spirit.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b779b9b5-f091-480b-8947-b3ae829359bb%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMounting%20financial%20losses%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESpirit%20first%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fread-spirit-airlines-open-letter-customers-bankruptcy-keep-flying-booking-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esought%20bankruptcy%20protection%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20November%202024%2C%20following%20years%20of%20mounting%20financial%20losses%20and%20the%20collapse%20of%20a%20proposed%20%243.8%20billion%20merger%20deal%20with%20JetBlue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20budget%20airline%2C%20easily%20recognizable%20by%20its%20bright%20yellow%20planes%2C%20reported%20in%20its%20initial%20voluntary%20bankruptcy%20petition%20that%20as%20of%20September%20that%20year%2C%20it%20had%20%249.49%20billion%20in%20total%20assets%20and%20%248.99%20billion%20in%20total%20debts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpirit%20emerged%20from%20bankruptcy%20in%20March%20last%20year%20after%20the%20airline%20said%20it%20slashed%20%24800%20million%20in%20debt%20and%20received%20a%20%24350%20million%20equity%20infusion%20from%20existing%20investors%20%26quot%3Bto%20support%20Spirit's%20future%20initiatives%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20the%20rebound%20was%20short-lived.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Commission%20quarterly%20report%20filed%20last%20August%2C%20the%20airline's%20parent%20company%2C%20Spirit%20Aviation%20Holdings%2C%20warned%20it%20may%20not%20be%20able%20to%20stay%20in%20business%20another%20year.%20Later%20that%20month%2C%20the%20airline%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspirit-airlines-filed-for-second-ba