attractions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226263%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22TRain%20driving%20through%20fall%20foliage%20in%20lake%20district%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a20bc2d3e2f1aef369b6ae%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224179%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20train%20driving%20through%20the%20Lake%20District%20in%20the%20fall.%3Cp%3Eby%20Andrea%20Pucci%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETucked%20between%20rolling%20fells%20(grassy%20hills)%20and%20England's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthousands-people-walk-over-largest-lake-balaton-central-europe-2017-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elargest%20lake%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20same%20name%2C%20the%20town%20of%20Windermere%20feels%20like%20its%20own%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHome%20to%20fewer%20than%2010%2C000%20residents%2C%20it's%20small%20enough%20to%20cross%20on%20foot%20yet%20expansive%20in%20feel.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20surrounding%20hills%20and%20lake%20feel%20quietly%20confident.%20They%20soften%20the%20skyline%20and%20set%20a%20slower%20pace%2C%20making%20it%20clear%20this%20isn't%20a%20place%20built%20for%20rushing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20this%20gives%20Windermere%20a%20wonderfully%20quiet%2C%20oasis-like%20rhythm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20feeling%20removed%20from%20the%20hustle%20and%20bustle%2C%20it's%20surprisingly%20well-connected%20and%20close%20enough%20to%20reach%20without%20much%20fuss.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20short%20drive%20from%20cities%20like%20Lancaster%20and%20Carlisle.%20By%20train%2C%20it's%20three%20hours%20from%20London%2C%20an%20hour%20and%20a%20half%20from%20Manchester%2C%20and%20two%20or%20three%20hours%20from%20Edinburgh.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20in%20the%20county%20of%20Cumbria%2C%20which%20has%20something%20for%20everyone%2C%20whether%20you%20want%20to%20partake%20in%20watersports%20and%20hiking%2C%20visit%20Scafell%20Pike%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fengland-yorkshire-three-peaks-challenge-worth-it-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EEngland's%20highest%20mountain%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20a%20war%20memorial)%2C%20try%20local%20specialties%20like%20sticky%20toffee%20pudding%20and%20Cumberland%20sausage%2C%20or%20just%20seek%20out%20some%20serenity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225403%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tall%20green%20mountains%2C%20peaceful%20lakes%20in%20lake%20district%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a5c0abd3e2f1aef369cf93%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223602%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFleetwith%20Pike%20and%20Buttermere%20in%20the%20English%20Lake%20District.%3Cp%3EWhitcombeRD%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20some%20of%20our%20most%20cherished%20Lake%20District%20moments%20have%20come%20from%20serene%20walks%20and%20hikes%20around%20the%20lakes%20and%20fells%20of%20Windermere%20and%20nearby%20towns%2C%20as%20well%20as%20leisurely%20cruises%20and%20visits%20to%20the%20world-famous%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpeter-rabbit-author-beatrix-potters-cottage-available-to-rent-2015-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBeatrix%20Potter%3C%2Fa%3E%20attractions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20though%20many%20of%20its%20local%20caf%C3%A9s%20have%20small-town%20charm%2C%20this%20area%20has%20serious%20food%20cred%2C%20too.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flake-district-unesco-world-heritage-site-2017-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EThe%20Lake%20District%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20home%20to%20several%20Michelin-starred%20restaurants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20so%2C%20unlike%20busier%20hot%20spots%2C%20Windermere%20has%20retained%20its%20identity%20and%20sense%20of%20self.%20It%20is%20protective%20of%20its%20pace%2C%20its%20peace%2C%20its%20essence.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20here%20seem%20to%20look%20out%20for%20each%20other.%20They%20don't%20just%20nod%20as%20they%20pass%3B%20they%20stop%20to%20chat%20and%20remember%20people's%20names.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%205%3A30%20p.m.%2C%20many%20shops%20and%20caf%C3%A9s%20close%2C%20while%20a%20handful%20of%20restaurants%2C%20pubs%2C%20and%20the%20local%20Sainsbury's%20stay%20open%20late.%20Even%20at%20night%2C%20the%20town%20feels%20safe%20and%20calm%2C%20especially%20compared%20to%20larger%20cities.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227b3ef0ef-51ba-40a0-a90b-e796887a545c%5C%22%3EI%20dream%20of%20living%20here%20someday%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20places%20are%20lovely%20to%20visit%2C%20but%20Windermere%20feels%20like%20somewhere%20that%20meets%20you%20exactly%20where%20you%20are%2C%20offering%20something%20for%20every%20stage%20of%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20all%20these%20years%2C%20I%20still%20sometimes%20feel%20that%20same%20stillness%20I%20felt%20on%20our%20very%20first%20trip%20when%20I%20was%20sitting%20by%20the%20water%20and%20realizing%20we'd%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsingles-trip-bali-south-asian-love-desi-love-island-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efound%20somewhere%20special%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20visit%20has%20marked%20a%20different%20chapter%20in%20our%20family's%20lives%2C%20from%20being%20pregnant%20with%20a%20toddler%20in%20tow%20to%20returning%20with%20teenagers%20who%20now%20set%20their%20own%20pace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESomehow%2C%20though%2C%20Windermere%20has%20grown%20with%20us%2C%20and%20I%20often%20wonder%20what%20it%20might%20feel%20like%20if%20we%20stayed%20a%20little%20longer.%20After%20all%2C%20there's%20something%20comforting%20and%20restorative%20about%20living%20where%20nature%20is%20such%20a%20big%20part%20of%20daily%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20imagine%20where%20I'd%20call%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-and-uk-life-biggest-differences-after-moving-home-space-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehome%20in%20the%20UK%3