0from%20random%20strangers%20I%20never%20see%20again.%20But%20one%20act%20of%20kindness%20led%20to%20a%20lot%20more%20than%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225918c37c-b0c4-4416-8b8d-dd057b29b860%5C%22%3EA%20stranger%20offered%20me%20a%20double%20stroller%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20my%20third%20child%20was%20born%2C%20he%20hated%20being%20in%20the%20stroller%20and%20insisted%20on%20being%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmilitary-inspired-baby-carrier-is-also-a-backpack-2017-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebaby%20sling%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20walking%20home%20up%20a%20steep%20hill%20with%20my%20oldest%20on%20the%20buggy%20board%20and%20my%20middle%20child%20in%20the%20stroller.%20The%20baby%20was%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparenting-editor-mom-of-twins-shares-her-favorite-twin-products-2022-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebaby%20carrier%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20my%20back%20was%20aching.%20It%20was%20raining%20cats%20and%20dogs%2C%20and%20we%20were%20all%20drenched.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221206%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Woman%20babywearing%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a6fdfafd4fbd083f2969c2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22905%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author's%20third%20child%20did%20not%20like%20riding%20on%20a%20stroller.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20peripheral%20vision%2C%20I%20saw%20someone%20in%20a%20car%20waving%20at%20me%2C%20assuming%20they%20were%20going%20to%20ask%20for%20directions%2C%20I%20walked%20toward%20them.%20A%20lovely%20woman%20wound%20the%20window%20down%20and%20asked%20if%20I%20wanted%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhaving-twins-is-not-more-expensive-than-two-children-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edouble%20stroller%3C%2Fa%3E.%20She%20said%20she%20saw%20me%20walking%20up%20and%20down%20the%20hill%20a%20lot%20and%20was%20worried%20about%20my%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20surprised%2C%20but%20I%20said%20yes.%20The%20next%20day%2C%20I%20nervously%20went%20to%20collect%20it%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fbest-chocolate%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebox%20of%20chocolates%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We%20had%20a%20wonderful%20conversation%20and%20instantly%20connected.%20We%20exchanged%20numbers%2C%20and%20she%20invited%20me%20over%20for%20breakfast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221206%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Women%20posing%20for%20selfie%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a6f74cd3e2f1aef369dffe%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22905%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20stranger%20offered%20the%20author%20(black%20shirt)%20a%20double%20stroller%2C%20and%20they%20became%20instant%20friends.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20how%20I%20met%20my%20friend%2C%20Salma.%20Salma%20is%20an%20amazing%20cook%2C%20and%20the%20huevos%20rancheros%20for%20breakfast%20were%20amazing.%20She%20even%20made%20mint%20tea%20from%20scratch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b618aed5-a637-45d0-b3ea-32eec4782caa%5C%22%3EIt%20was%20hard%20to%20make%20friends%20as%20a%20mom%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20time%20we%20met%20up%2C%20we%20were%20going%20to%20a%20coffee%20shop%2C%20but%20we%20met%20at%20the%20library%20first.%20I%20was%20saying%20goodbye%20to%20my%20friend%2C%20Nadia%2C%20whom%20I%20met%20when%20our%20oldest%20children%20went%20to%20preschool%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20totally%20out%20of%20my%20depth%20when%20my%20oldest%20started%20preschool.%20It%20is%20such%20a%20sociable%20time%2C%20but%20I%20did%20not%20know%20how%20to%20make%20friends%20with%20the%20other%20moms.%20Most%20of%20them%20had%20older%20children%20who%20had%20been%20at%20the%20school%20for%20years%2C%20and%20they%20were%20all%20friends.%20It%20felt%20impenetrable.%20Other%20moms%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworking-mom-unread-emails-give-up-inbox-zero-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eworking%20moms%3C%2Fa%3E%20rushing%20to%20office%20jobs%2C%20while%20I%20worked%20from%20home%20as%20a%20freelance%20writer.%20Nadia%20was%20my%20savior.%20A%20down-to-earth%2C%20genuine%2C%20and%20kind%20person%20who%20came%20from%20the%20same%20part%20of%20Scotland%20as%20me.%20Since%20we%20became%20friends%2C%20we%20have%20had%20two%20more%20children%20each%2C%20bringing%20our%20total%20to%20four.%20Our%20children%20have%20grown%20up%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221206%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mexican%20food%20made%20my%20mom%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a7020cfd4fbd083f296a47%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22905%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author's%20friend%20cooks%20fo%20her.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20fateful%20day%2C%20it%20felt%20too%20weird%20to%20leave%20Nadia%20behind.%20I%20looked%20at%20Salma%2C%20and%20she%20said%20Nadia%20should%20come%20too.%20We%20quickly%20realized%20how%20much%20we%20all%20had%20in%20common.%20We%20don't%20talk%20enough%20about%20how%20friendship%20is%20about%20chemistry.%20It%20is%20something%20you%20cannot%20explain.%20We%20all%20lived%20in%20the%20same%20area.%20That%20is%20the%20thing%20about%20motherhood%2C%20it%20is%20not%20enough%20on%20its%20own%20to%20bind.%20You%20have%20to%20genuinely%20like%20each%20other.%20Our%20trio%20was%20born.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e25f73e0-baf8-4f5a-9f15-9a1c6a779cf5%5C%22%3EWe%20support%20each%20other%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMotherhood%20was%20never%20supposed%20to%20be%20done%20alone%2C%20and%20thanks%20to%20Nadia%20and%20Salma%2C%20it%20never%20has%20been.%20But%20we%20are%20more%20than%20just%20mothers.%20More%20than%20our%20children.%20When%20one%20of%20us%20passes%20a%20test%20or%20achieves%20something%20career-wise%2C%20we%20celebrate%20that%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20one%20big%20birthday%2C%20Nadia%20bought%20me%20beautiful%20earrings%2C%20and%20they%20remind%20me%20of%20our%20beautiful%20friendship%20every%20time%20I%20wear%20them.%20There%20is%20something%20about%20knowing%20that%20these%20women%20have%20my%20back%2C%20that%20we%20have%20created%20this%20little%20village%20between%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221206%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Close%20up%20of%20earrings%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a6fdaf1fb3fcb42648cef8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22905%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author's%20new%20friend%20gifted%20her%20a%20pair%20of%20earrings.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20all%20had%20a%20fourth%20child%20since%20we%20first%20became%20friends%2C%20and%20Salma%20came%20round%20with%20delicious%20food.%20I%20never%20had%20that%20with%20my%20other%20babies%2C%20and%20it%20made%20such%20a%20difference.%20Nadia%20was%20thoughtful%20enough%20to%20buy%20lots%20of%20baby%20clothes%2C%20which%20saved%20my%20life%20many%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20friendship%20means%20that%20not%20only%20are%20we%20growing%20up%20together%2C%20but%20so%20are%20our%20children.%20As%20our%20families%20grow%20together%2C%20we%20troubleshoot%20together.%20Asking%20for%20advice%20and%20reassurance.%20The%20emotional%20support%20makes%20all%20the%20difference.%20We%20keep%20each%20other%20sane%20through%20Instagram%20Reels%20and%20sage%20advice.%20I%20know%20they%20have%20my%20back%20and%20that%20if%20anything%20serious%20happened%2C%20they%20would%20be%20there%20for%20me.%20Ditto%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20don't%20talk%20enough%20about%20how%20hard%20it%20is%20to%20make%20and%20keep%20friends.%20Life%20always%20gets%20in%20the%20way%20despite%20our%20good%20intentions.%20Having%20two%20good%20friends%20who%20are%20also%20friends%20with%20each%20other%20makes%20me%20feel%20like%20the%20luckiest%20woman%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstranger-gave-me-stroller-found-mom-friendship-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773496441000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a70b9ad3e2f1aef369e31f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstranger-gave-me-stroller-found-mom-friendship-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20met%20one%20mom%20through%20a%20random%20act%20of%20kindness%2C%20and%20together%20we%20built%20the%20support%20system%20every%20mother%20needs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Catherine%20Balavage)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstranger-gave-me-stroller-found-mom-friendship-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Iran%20allowed%20some%20Indian%20vessels%20through%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz%3A%20Envoy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773495294000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2025-06%2F19%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F1200X630%2F1750314570-7227.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fworld-news%2Firan-allowed-indian-vessels-through-strait-of-hormuz-envoy-126031400642_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Iran's%20Ambassador%20to%20India%20Mohammad%20Fathali%20noted%20historical%20relations%20between%20the%20two%20nations%2C%20and%20said%20that%20both%20sides%20have%20maintained%20cooperation%20through%20the%20conflict%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fworld-news%2Firan-allowed-indian-vessels-through-strait-of-hormuz-envoy-12