onths%20into%20my%20second%20marriage%2C%20I%20became%20pregnant%20with%20our%20first%20child.%20As%20it%20turned%20out%2C%20that%20earlier%20diagnosis%20did%20not%20prevent%20me%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freference%2Fhow-to-get-pregnant%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egetting%20pregnant%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20cause%20any%20complications.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20initially%20did%20not%20want%20children%2C%20and%20he%20took%20the%20news%20hard%20at%20first.%20But%20then%20he%20surprised%20me.%20He%20embraced%20the%20idea%20of%20fatherhood%20more%20fully%20than%20I%20could%20have%20imagined.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERaising%20our%20daughter%20has%20been%20challenging%20in%20all%20the%20ways%20people%20warn%20you%20it%20will%20be.%20It%20is%20exhausting%2C%20relentless%2C%20and%20humbling.%20But%20it%20has%20also%20changed%20us%20irrevocably.%20She%20made%20our%20lives%20bigger.%20She%20turned%20ordinary%20days%20into%20an%20adventure%2C%20even%20when%20we%20are%20running%20on%20fumes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20why%20one%20night%2C%20when%20I%20was%20weepily%20looking%20at%20her%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-regrets-only-having-silly-snapchat-filter-photos-baby-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebaby%20photos%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20turned%20to%20my%20husband%20and%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3BWhen%20can%20we%20have%20another%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20shot%20it%20down%20as%20quickly%20as%20he%20could.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20want%20any%20more%20kids%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BShe's%20perfect%20for%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20we%20have%20had%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-handle-conflicts-disagreements-with-coworkers-at-work-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edifficult%20conversation%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20hundred%20more%20times%2C%20and%20his%20answer%20has%20stayed%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22aa679012-f531-4e35-a5cd-8efb7328e7d4%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI've%20had%20to%20create%20a%20safe%20space%20to%20talk%20this%20through%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20question%20of%20having%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-planning-one-and-done-pressure-to-have-more-kids-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esecond%20child%3C%2Fa%3E%20isn't%20an%20easy%20one%20to%20answer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20common%20challenge%20for%20couples%2C%26quot%3B%20Amber%20Trueblood%2C%20a%20licensed%20marriage%20therapist%2C%20told%20me%20recently%20when%20I%20told%20her%20about%20our%20rift.%20%26quot%3BParenthood%20is%20hard%20on%20a%20marriage%2C%20and%20for%20some%20partners%2C%20the%20idea%20of%20doing%20everything%20all%20over%20again%20isn't%20exciting.%20It's%20terrifying.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hardest%20part%20for%20me%20is%20that%20my%20desire%20feels%20so%20clear.%20I%20can%20picture%20another%20child%20in%20our%20family.%20I%20can%20picture%20our%20daughter%20with%20a%20sibling.%20I%20can%20picture%20the%20kind%20of%20home%20I%20thought%20we%20were%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20my%20husband's%20no%20is%20not%20coming%20from%20nowhere%2C%20and%20neither%20is%20my%20yes.%20Trueblood%20reminded%20me%20that%20in%20most%20couples%2C%20there%20are%20real%20reasons%20underneath%20each%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPerhaps%20one%20partner%20feels%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F401k-hardship-withdrawals-record-retirement-savings-investment-accounts-stock-market-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efinancial%20pressure%20%3C%2Fa%3Eor%20fears%20passing%20on%20a%20genetic%20anomaly%2C%20rendering%20them%20incapable%20of%20imagining%20the%20benefits%20of%20having%20another%20child%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BOr%20one%20partner%20fears%20raising%20their%20only%20child%20without%20siblings%20because%20of%20their%20own%20very%20special%20sibling%20relationships%2C%20rendering%20them%20incapable%20of%20imagining%20raising%20an%20only%20child%20in%20a%20happy%20and%20complete%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20do%20not%20know%20if%20that%20applies%20to%20us%2C%20but%20I'm%20now%20trying%20to%20broach%20the%20subject%20from%20a%20new%20angle%3A%20explaining%20to%20each%20other%20why%20we%20want%20what%20we%20want.%20Trueblood%20explained%20that%20when%20neither%20person%20feels%20pressured%20and%20can%20openly%20share%20their%20beliefs%2C%20the%20conversation%20can%20shift.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22502%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Claire%20Volkman%20and%20her%20daughter%20kissing%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b41e08a96e437d6eb8443f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22837%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20is%20now%20prioritizing%20her%20daughter.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Claire%20Volkman%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWithout%20feeling%20that%20pressure%2C%20each%20person%20is%20much%20better%20able%20to%20absorb%20and%20explore%20both%20their%20own%20feelings%20and%20their%20partner's%20feelings%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BYou%20may%20find%20a%20shift%20happens%20in%20one%20or%20both%20partners%20if%20neither%20feels%20they%20are%20being%20challenged%20or%20manipulated.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227a4e2a9c-8312-4ef0-a56a-fbf5fae15548%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20debated%20leaving%2C%20but%20I'm%20staying%20no%20matter%20what%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EShould%20I%20leave%3F%20This%20is%20the%20question%20I%20do%20not%20want%20to%20ask%2C%20but%20it%20is%20there.%20There%20really%20isn't%20a%20compromise%20that%20gives%20both%20people%20what%20they%20want.%20You%20either%20have%20another%20child%20or%20you%20do%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrueblood%20told%20me%20that%20in%20these%20situations%2C%20partners%20have%20to%20ask%20themselves%20a%20hard%20thing%20honestly.%20%26quot%3BCan%20I%20release%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquit-my-corporate-job-over-text-after-burning-out-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efrustration%20and%20resentment%3C%2Fa%3E%20toward%20my%20partner%20so%20that%20we%20may%20have%20a%20strong%2C%20healthy%2C%20loving%20relationship%20moving%20forward%20and%20a%20happy%20home%20for%20our%20current%20child(ren)%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20some%20people%2C%20the%20decision%20is%20straightforward.%20They%20want%20another%20kid%2C%20their%20partner%20does%20not%2C%20and%20they%20are%20not%20willing%20to%20negotiate.%20Other%20people%20find%20ways%20to%20feel%20fulfilled%20in%20the%20life%20they%20have%2C%20or%20hope%20feelings%20shift%20as%20their%20child%20grows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20I've%20found%20fulfillment%20in%20relishing%20my%20one%20child%20and%20spoiling%20her%20in%20ways%20I%20couldn't%20do%20with%20multiple.%20Pouring%20into%20my%20daughter%20has%20helped%20a%20lot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20still%20a%20little%20hurt%2C%20and%20my%20heart%20aches%20every%20time%20someone%20I%20know%20announces%20a%20pregnancy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20book%20isn't%20over%2C%20though%2C%20and%20it's%20a%20conversation%20we%20sometimes%20broach%20when%20tensions%20are%20very%20low.%20Whether%20we%20end%20up%20with%20more%20or%20live%20with%20just%20our%20perfect%20one%2C%20I%20know%20it%20will%20be%20the%20right%20decision%20for%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENavigating%20this%20struggle%20together%20is%20a%20testament%20to%20the%20strength%20of%20our%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwife-want-another-child-husband-doesnt-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773490621000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b41dbca7a4f9df67ba4a55%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwife-want-another