%20stuck%20in%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20senior%20year%20of%20college%2C%20all%20my%20friends%20were%20either%20living%20in%20the%20dorms%20or%20in%20their%20own%20places%2C%20but%20I%20was%20still%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20as%20I%20entered%20my%20final%20year%20of%20school%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20start%20looking%20for%20a%20place%20of%20my%20own%2C%20without%20my%20parents'%20assistance.%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20would%20never%20truly%20consider%20myself%20a%20real%20%26quot%3Badult%26quot%3B%20unless%20I%20took%20on%20the%20process%20by%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20few%20touring%20mishaps%2C%20the%20third%20apartment%20building%20I%20visited%20seemed%20like%20the%20perfect%20fit.%20It%20wasn't%20furnished%20yet%2C%20but%20it%20already%20felt%20like%20home.%20It%20even%20had%20wooden%20floors%20that%20reminded%20me%20of%20the%20room%20I%20grew%20up%20in.%20I%20signed%20my%20lease%20one%20week%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221529%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20empty%20apartment%20with%20white%20walls%20and%20wooden%20floors.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b4351a4d65ec517529f8c0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221147%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20apartment%20felt%20like%20home%20before%20I%20even%20furnished%20it.%3Cp%3ECarrie%20Berk%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20I%20quickly%20became%20overwhelmed%20by%20the%20moving%20process.%20As%20I%20stared%20at%20boxes%20piled%20to%20the%20ceiling%2C%20I%20didn't%20know%20where%20to%20start.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20tackling%20the%20space%2C%20excited%20to%20see%20my%20NYC-style%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbefore-and-after-photos-of-hgtvs-barbie-dreamhouse-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBarbie%20Dream%20House%3C%2Fa%3E%20vision%20come%20to%20life.%20But%20the%20more%20I%20unpacked%2C%20the%20more%20things%20began%20to%20fall%20apart.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20matt