rget%20drone%20threats%20along%20the%20alliance's%20eastern%20edge%2C%20its%20border%20with%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThrough%20rapid%2090-day%20testing%20cycles%20designed%20to%20replicate%20real%20situations%2C%20US%20forces%2C%20Baltic%20allies%2C%20and%20defense%20companies%20are%20building%20a%20shared%20data%20network%20for%20faster%20decision-making.%20The%20effort%20links%20sensors%20that%20detect%20aerial%20threats%20with%20counter-drone%20systems%20that%20can%20destroy%20them%2C%20aiming%20to%20improve%20defenses%20against%20Russian-style%20drone%20attacks%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmerops-middle-east-iran-drones-shaheds-surveyor-us-military-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EShahed-type%20systems%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20and%20Estonian%20forces%20executed%20exercise%20Digital%20Shield%202.0%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20the%20second%20stage%20in%20an%20ongoing%20testing%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20exercise%20%26quot%3Bwas%20really%20born%20from%20an%20initiative%20to%20integrate%20different%20sensor%20types%20into%20an%20easily%20accessible%20and%20shareable%20integrated%20sensor%20architecture%2C%20or%20an%20air%20picture%2C%26quot%3B%20US%20Army%20Capt.%20Micah%20Maule%2C%20plans%20officer%20for%20the%2010th%20Army%20Air%20and%20Missile%20Defense%20Command%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20first%20Digital%20Shield%20proved%20the%20concept%2C%20the%20second%20expanded%20the%20scale%2C%20adding%20more%20sensors%20to%20detect%20larger%20uncrewed%20aerial%20systems%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Esuch%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Firan-russia-now-us-one-style-drone-reshaping-moden-war-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EShahed-type%20drones%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20additional%20air-defense%20and%20counter-UAS%20radars%20to%20sharpen%20the%20picture%20of%20incoming%20threats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20systems%20feed%20into%20a%20common%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-army-jammed-new-tech-ngc2-electronic-warfare-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecommand-and-control%20network%3C%2Fa%3E%20using%20commercially%20developed%20software%2C%20creating%20a%20streamlined%20flow%20of%20surveillance%20data%20that%20operators%20can%20view%20in%20a%20single%20air%20picture%20before%20deciding%20how%20to%20respond.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20you%20could%20actually%20task%20effectors%20to%20go%20out%20and%20destroy%20drones%20from%20the%20same%20common%20operational%20picture%2C%26quot%3B%20Maule%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDigital%20Shield%202.0%20included%20several%20simulated%20scenarios%20that%20could%20become%20real-world%20threats%2C%20including%20cyberattacks%20disrupting%20operations%2C%20high-stress%20conditions%20with%20lots%20of%20drone%20targets%2C%20and%20a%20live-fire%20situation%20running%20the%20entire%20process%20against%20Shahed%20replicators.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227199%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20wearing%20camouflage%20stands%20next%20to%20a%20tall%20radar.%20A%20small%20white%20drone%20stands%20sits%20on%20the%20beach.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b445f6a7a4f9df67ba4f2f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224799%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20second%20testing%20involved%20various%20sensors%2C%20counter-drone%20interceptors%2C%20and%20Shahed%20replicators.%3Cp%3EUS%20Army%20photo%20by%20Maj.%20Alexander%20Watkins%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAdding%20more%20sensors%20layers%20the%20defenses%2C%20but%20it%20also%20increases%20the%20volume%20of%20incoming%20data.%20Maule%20said%20the%20goal%20of%20the%20shared%20command-and-control%20system%20is%20to%20merge%20those%20inputs%20into%20one%20clear%20picture%2C%20reducing%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Farmy-leaders-warn-modern-warfare-is-overwhelming-commanders-with-data-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecognitive%20burden%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eon%20operators.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20advantage%20of%20the%20design%20is%20that%20the%20system%20can%20be%20operated%20farther%20from%20the%20front%2C%20out%20of%20range%20of%20many%20types%20of%20drones%2C%20and%20that%20it%20feeds%20data%20to%20multiple%20partners%20for%20heightened%20awareness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rapid%20pace%20of%20the%20Digital%20Shield%20testing%20reflects%20the%20Pentagon's%20Silicon%20Valley-style%20%26quot%3Bmove%20fast%2C%20fail%20fast%2C%20fix%20fast%26quot%3B%20approach%20for%20developing%20new%20technology.%20It%20also%20pressures%20industry%20partners%20to%20keep%20up.%20Vendors%20must%20meet%20strict%20integration%20requirements%2C%20and%20the%20swift%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Edevelopment%20cycle%20forces%20faster%20fixes%20and%20upgrades%20based%20on%20field%20feedback.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDigital%20Shield%20is%20an%20example%20of%20the%20work%20being%20done%20as%20part%20of%20the%20new%20Eastern%20Flank%20Deterrence%20Line%20initiative%2C%20which%20is%20led%20by%20the%20US%20and%20NATO.%20The%20effort%20is%20intended%20to%20build%20a%20robust%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-war-teaching-nato-air-forces-lessons-fighting-russia-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edefense%20against%20Russia%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20can%20detect%20drones%20across%20wide%20areas%20and%20counter%20them%20with%20lower-cost%20solutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArtificial%20intelligence%20is%20also%20being%20integrated%20into%20the%20initiative%20to%20analyze%20sensor%20data%20faster%20and%20speed%20up%20decisions%20on%20how%20to%20respond.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20persistent%20problem%20remains%20the%20cost%20of%20stopping%20cheap%20drones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20to%20beat%20the%20cost%20curve%2C%26quot%3B%20Maule%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20UAS%20is%20a%20couple%20or%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20dollars%2C%20you%20can't%20be%20using%20extremely%20expensive%20interceptors.%26quot%3B%20The%20US%20and%20its%20allies%20have%20learned%20that%20lesson%20from%20Ukraine%20and%20in%20the%20Middle%20East.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-nato-linking-defenses-counter-drone-fight-on-russia-border-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773489721000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b44753a96e437d6eb84949%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-nato-linking-defenses-counter-drone-fight-on-russia-border-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22By%20linking%20different%20sensors%20and%20systems%2C%20the%20US%20and%20its%20allies%20will%20have%20a%20better%20air%20surveillance%20network%20for%20potential%20drone%20threats.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22cpanella%40businessinsider.com%20(Chris%20Panella)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-nato-linking-defenses-counter-drone-fight-on-russia-border-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20spent%20%2461%2C000%20building%20a%20personal%20pub%20in%20my%20backyard.%20There%20are%203%20mistakes%20I%20wish%20I%20hadn't%20made.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223284%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Stephen%20Hutyra%20inside%20his%20backyard%20pub.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b2c3bba96e437d6eb830b7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222463%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EStephen%20Hutyra.%3Cp%3EStephen%20Hutyra%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EStephen%20Hutyra%2C%2042%2C%20built%20a%20personal%20pub%20he%20calls%20The%20Thirsty%20Goat%20in%20his%20backyard.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20loves%20the%20space%2C%20but%20wishes%20he'd%20installed%20a%20hot-water%20heater%20for%20the%20bathroom%20and%20sinks.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20also%20could%20have%20benefited%20from%20a%20little%20more%20space%20behind%20the%20bar%20area.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Stephen%20Hutyra%2C%20a%2042-year-old%20program%20analyst%20living%20in%20the%20small%20town%20of%20West%2C%20Texas.%20It's%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20November%202020%2C%20I%20was%20inspired%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fman-creates-pub-in-his-backyard-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebuild%20a%20pub%20in%20my%20backyard%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20seeing%20a%20Facebook%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20a%20saying%20that%20everything%20is%20bigger%20and%20better%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fliberty-tiny-home-village-texas-downsizing-luxury-photos-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ein%20Texas%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20so%20I%20wanted%20our%20pub%20to%20be%20bigger%20and%20better%20than%20the%20one%20I%20saw%20in%20the%20pictures%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20spent%20three%20years%20and%20%2461%2C000%20building%20the%20space%20we%20call%20The%20Thirsty%20Goat%20on%20half%20an%20acre%20of%20land.%20A%20construction%20team%20built%20the%20structure%2C%20and%20I%20finished%20the%20work%20with%20my%20family's%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20family%2C%20friends%2C%20and%20I%20find%20ourselves%20sitting%20out%20here%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20week%20until%20midnight%2C%20or%20until%202%20or%203%20a.m.%20on%20the%20weekends.%20We've%20thoroughly%20enjoyed%20it%20since%20finishing%20back%20in%20August%2C%20but%20we're%20only%20just%20starting%20to%20see%20how%20much%20we'll%20use%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20there%20are%20a%20few%20things%20I%20wish%20I'd%20done%20differently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Inside%20the%20pub%20Stephen%20Hutyra%20built%20in%20his%20backyard.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b2dbc8a7a4f9df67ba3ad0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EInside%20the%20pub%20Stephen%20Hutyra%20built%20in%20his%20backyard.%3Cp%3EStephen%20Hutyra%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bc65ba3c-e21a-4a82-81cd-0db1426587d6%5C%22%3EI%20should've%20connected%20a%20hot-water%20heater%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20mistake%20I%20made%20is%20something%20that%20my%20wife%20reminds%20me%20of%20all%20the%20time%3A%20I%20didn't%20hook%20up%20hot%20water%20to%20the%20bathroom%20or%20the%20bar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20only%20cold%20water%20coming%20out%20of%20both%20sinks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20think%20I'd%20have%20the%20space%20for%20a%20hot-water%20heater%2C%20but%20I%20probably%20could%20have%20gotten%20one%20of%20those%20little%20tankless%20ones%20and%20put%20it%20on%20the%20outside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20wouldn't%20have%20taken%20much%20to%20add%20that%20on%2C%20and%20it's%20been%20very%20cold%20washing%20hands%20and%20dishes%20in%20the%20winter%2C%20so%20I%20regret%20not%20doing%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20bathroom%20inside%20Stephen%20Hutyra's%20backyard%20pub.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b1c9ed4d65ec517529daf2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20bathroom%20inside%20Stephen%20Hutyra's%20backyard%20pub.%3Cp%3EStephen%20Hutyra%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224c3f7fd3-2526-46ec-961a-aa600954fc7e%5C%22%3EUnfortunately%2C%20I%20didn't%20install%20a%20dishwasher%20either%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20another%20thing%20my%20wife%20reminds%20me%20of%20all%20the%20time.%20I%20should%20have%20planned%20to%20install%20a%20small%20dishwasher%20below%20the%20cabinet%20that%20sits%20behind%20the%20bar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20either%20have%20to%20wash%20dishes%20with%20cold%20water%20in%20the%20bar%20sink%20or%20load%20dirty%20glassware%20into%20a%20tub%20I%20haul%20into%20the%20house%20to%20wash%20in%20the%20dishwasher.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20a%20dishwasher%20would%20really%20come%20in%20handy%20to%20load%20dirty%20dishes%20and%20cutlery%20throughout%20the%20day%20and%20night.%20But%20with%20the%20compact%20floor%20plan%20I%20mapped%20out%2C%20I%20just%20didn't%20have%20the%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20cabinets%20and%20sink%20in%20Stephen%20Hutyra's%20backyard%20pub.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b2db264d65ec517529e621%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20countertop%20area%20of%20the%20pub.%3Cp%3EStephen%20Hutyra%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22db2a0bc6-bbec-4183-988f-0ae5ab1fa43e%5C%22%3EA%20little%20extra%20space%20behind%20the%20bar%20would%20have%20been%20nice%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20I%20only%20planned%20to%20put%20one%20mini%20fridge%20behind%20the%20bar.%20After%20I%20installed%20it%2C%20though%2C%20I%20measured%20the%20space%20left%20and%20realized%20I%20had%20enough%20room%20for%20a%20second%20fridge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20two%20has%20really%20made%20a%20big%20impact.%20I%20frequently%20use%20the%20second%20to%20store%20juices%2C%20lemons%2C%20limes%2C%20and%20other%20items%20for%20mixed%20drinks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I%20didn't%20have%20the%20fridge%2C%20I'd%20probably%20have%20to%20use%20a%20small%20cooler%20with%20ice%20packs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20I%20didn't%20realize%2C%20though%2C%20is%20that%20because%20the%20countertop%20edge%20extends%20into%20that%20corner%2C%20the%20door%20to%20the%20second%20mini%20fridge%20can%20only%20open%20about%20halfway.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I%20had%20installed%20shelves%20there%20as%20I%20initially%20planned%2C%20there%20wouldn't%20be%20an%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20two%20mini%