96070b45%5C%22%3EMy%20life%20in%20Thailand%20costs%20less%2C%20I%20get%20more%2C%20and%20I'm%20happier%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMoving%20to%20a%20new%20country%20alone%20and%20starting%20my%20own%20business%20was%20terrifying%2C%20but%20I%20knew%20it%20would%20eventually%20give%20me%20the%20financial%20independence%20I%20couldn't%20find%20in%20the%20UK.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20that%20I'm%20my%20own%20boss%2C%20I%20still%20work%20hard.%20But%20the%20difference%20is%20that%20I'm%20building%20something%20for%20myself.%20In%20the%20eight%20months%20I've%20lived%20in%20Bangkok%2C%20my%20client%20base%20has%20grown.%20I%20earn%20slightly%20less%2C%20but%20my%20money%20stretches%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20rent%20my%20own%20condominium%20for%20%24500%20a%20month%2C%20which%20includes%20a%20swimming%20pool%2C%20a%20gym%2C%20and%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-work-coworking-space-with-on-site-preschool-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecoworking%20space%3C%2Fa%3E.%20My%20electricity%20bill%20is%20%2440%20a%20month%2C%20and%20water%20costs%20just%20%242.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThings%20that%20once%20felt%20like%20luxury%20in%20the%20UK%20are%20now%20part%20of%20my%20everyday%20life.%20I%20buy%20fresh%20fruit%20from%20local%20markets.%20I%20pay%20%246%20an%20hour%20for%20a%20weekly%20cleaner.%20I%20don't%20cook%3B%20I%20eat%20out%20every%20day%20without%20calculating%20whether%20I%20should%20skip%20it%20to%20save%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGetting%20around%20is%20affordable%2C%20too.%20I%20no%20longer%20own%20a%20car.%20A%20train%20journey%20costs%20around%20%241%2C%20and%20bike%20rental%20rides%20start%20at%20%241.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20moving%20to%20Thailand%2C%20I've%20embraced%20what%20the%20Thais%20call%20%26quot%3Bsabai%20sabai%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20a%20stress-free%20way%20of%20life.%20For%20the%20first%20time%20in%20years%2C%20I%20feel%20fulfilled%2C%20financially%20free%2C%20and%20happy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20ar