n%20Joseph%20for%20Sotheby's%20International%20Realty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfterward%2C%20Marianne%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20money%20remains%20%26quot%3Bavailable%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20declined%20to%20give%20details%2C%20saying%20the%20bankruptcy%20court%20%26quot%3Bnever%20gave%20me%20a%20number.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20phone%20interview%20on%20Thursday%2C%20she%20accused%20the%20trustee%20of%20lying%2C%20forgery%2C%20breaking%20into%20her%20home%2C%20intentionally%20damaging%20the%20home%20to%20collect%20%244%20million%20in%20insurance%2C%20and%20colluding%20with%20the%20%26quot%3Bcrooked%26quot%3B%20judge%20%E2%80%94%20and%20possibly%20with%20the%20Chinese%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20whole%20thing%20smells%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BEverything%20has%20been%20done%20illegally.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20she%20filed%2075%20pages%20of%20additional%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eprotests%20at%20the%20court%20in%20Lower%20Manhattan%2C%20asking%20for%20more%20time%20and%20resurrecting%20arguments%20repeatedly%20rejected%20by%20the%20judge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20understanding%20is%20a%20decision%20is%20not%20an%20order%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20one%2C%20adding%20in%20handwriting%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20entered%20a%20correct%20bid.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22928%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22This%20view%20of%20the%20Cassini%20mansion's%20second%20floor%20library%20shows%20its%20wood%20and%20marble%20paneling%20and%20one%20of%20two%20windows%20overlooking%2063rd%20Street.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69987539a645d1188189aa57%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22692%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Cassini%20mansion's%20library%20overlooks%2063rd%20Street.%3Cp%3EEvan%20Joseph%20for%20Sotheby's%20International%20Realty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20week%2C%20Togut%2C%