nt%20Jacqueline%20Kennedy%20when%20she%20was%20first%20lady.%3Cp%3EEvan%20Joseph%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Cassini%20died%2C%20an%20extended%20battle%20began%20over%20the%20late%20designer's%20fortune%20that%20continues%20to%20this%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%202016%2C%20a%20surrogate%20judge%20on%20Long%20Island%20had%20removed%20Marianne%20as%20executor%2C%20citing%20mismanagement%2C%20a%20claim%20she%20denies.%20Cassini's%20clothing%20and%20perfume%20lines%20were%20court-ordered%20out%20of%20the%20sisters'%20hands%20and%20into%20receivership.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20widow%20owes%20more%20than%20%24133%20million%20in%20civil%20judgments%2C%20attorneys%20in%20that%20case%20said%20in%20a%202024%20court%20filing.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20bullshit%2C%26quot%3B%20Marianne%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fashion%20heiress%20was%20also%20jailed%20%26quot%3Bfor%20refusals%20to%20comply%20with%20court%20orders%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20receiver%20also%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20she%20was%20thrown%20in%20jail%2C%20Marianne%20said%20in%20response%20%E2%80%94%20by%20another%20%26quot%3Bcrooked%26quot%3B%20judge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225301%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Oleg%20Cassini%20and%20Marianne%20Nestor%20attend%20a%20Manhattan%20fundraiser%20in%201975%2C%20four%20years%20after%20their%20secret%20marriage.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b46c20a7a4f9df67ba5478%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%227811%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOleg%20Cassini%20and%20Marianne%20Nestor%20attend%20a%20Manhattan%20fundraiser%20in%201975%2C%20four%20years%20after%20their%20secret%20marriage.%3Cp%3ELynn%20Karlin%2FWWD%2FPenske%20Media%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20estate%20battle%20dragged%20on%2C%20debts%20against%20the%20Manhattan%20townhouse%20started%20coming%20due.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeggy%20Nestor%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbankruptcies-across-economy-small-business-households-corporate-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efiled%20for%20bankruptcy%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202023%2C%20one%20day%20before%20a%20state%20judge%20in%20New%20York%20scheduled%20a%20sale%20of%20the%20townhouse%20to%20repay%20%2417%20million%20in%20mortgage%20arrears.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bankruptcy%20bought%20the%20Nestors%20another%20two%20years%20in%20the%20townhouse%2C%20which%20they%20promised%20to%20sell%20before%20ghosting%20and%20then%20suing%20their%20attorney.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20repeatedly%20insisted%20that%20they%20were%20too%20old%20to%20be%20evicted%20and%20that%20their%20rights%20as%20tenants%20were%20protected%20by%20New%20York's%20rent-stabilization%20laws%20%E2%80%94%20claims%20shot%20down%20multiple%20times%20in%20federal%20bankruptcy%20court%20and%20by%20appellate%20judges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20two%20weeks%20before%20Wednesday's%20final%20sign-off%2C%20the%20sisters%20made%20further%20attempts%20to%20foil%20the%20proceedings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20included%20accusing%20Togut%20in%20court%20papers%20of%20theft%20and%20incompetence%2C%20calling%20the%20sale%20a%20%26quot%3Bset%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20threatening%20to%20seek%20%26quot%3Btreble%20damages%2C%20which%20are%20in%20the%20millions%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20requesting%20the%20bankruptcy's%20%26quot%3Bremoval%20from%20Your%20Honor's%20court.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENeither%20sister%20was%20present%20for%20Wednesday's%20liquidation%20approval%2C%20though%20the%20judge%20noted%20on%20the%20record%20that%20both%20had%20been%20there%20minutes%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20were%20filing%20more%20papers%2C%20he%20said%2C%20and%20complaining%20to%20court%20staff%20that%20they%20needed%20to%20rush%20back%20to%20the%20townhouse%20%26quot%3Bto%20call%20the%20police%20or%20the%20FBI%26quot%3B%20to%20stop%20an%20in-progress%20moving%20of%20%26quot%3Btheir%26quot%3B%20items%20out%20of%20the%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20is%20an%20absurd%20contention%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20judge%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20Marianne%20Nestor%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20she%20did%20call%20the%20police%20and%20the%20FBI.%20She%20is%20waiting%20for%20a%20call%20back%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgilded-age-manhattan-townhouse-oleg-cassini-fashion-heiress-bankruptcy-battle-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773486001000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b45f324d65ec517529fddd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgilded-age-manhattan-townhouse-oleg-cassini-fashion-heiress-bankruptcy-battle-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22They're%20in%20their%2080s%20and%20have%20no%20lawyer.%20That's%20not%20stopping%20two%20sisters%20from%20a%20spirited%20battle%20to%20reclaim%20their%20Gilded%20Age%20Manhattan%20townhouse.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22litaliano%40insider.com%20(Laura%20Italiano)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgilded-age-manhattan-townhouse-oleg-cassini-fashion-heiress-bankruptcy-battle-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Former%20Uber%20CEO%20Travis%20Kalanick%20said%20he%20moved%20to%20Texas%2C%20joining%20a%20growing%20list%20of%20tech%20billionaires%20leaving%20California%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222065%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Former%20Uber%20Technologies%20Inc.%20CEO%20and%20co-founder%20Travis%20Kalanick%20at%20NYSE%20during%20the%20company's%20IPO%20in%20New%20York%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b49cd7a7a4f9df67ba5910%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221377%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETravis%20Kalanick%2C%20former%20Uber%20CEO%2C%20has%20moved%20from%20California%20to%20Texas%20by%20the%20end%20of%202025.%3Cp%3EREUTERS%2FAndrew%20Kelly%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETravis%20Kalanick%2C%20former%20Uber%20CEO%2C%20moved%20from%20California%20to%20Texas%2C%20he%20said%20on%20%26quot%3BTBPN.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EKalanick%20joins%20other%20tech%20billionaires%20like%20Elon%20Musk%20in%20relocating%20to%20Texas%20from%20California.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETexas%20is%20attracting%20tech%20giants%20with%20favorable%20tax%20rates%20and%20business%20regulations.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20tech%20billionaire%20has%20left%20California%20for%20Texas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20on%20%26quot%3BTBPN%26quot%3B%20on%20Friday%2C%20former%20Uber%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftravis-kalanick-ex-uber-misfits-entering-robotics-game-atoms-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETravis%20Kalanick%3C%2Fa%3E%20told%20show%20hosts%20John%20Coogan%20and%20Jordi%20Hays%20that%20he%20moved%20to%20Texas%20at%20the%20end%20of%202025%2C%20when%20asked%20if%20Kalanick%20would%20like%20to%20come%20back%20to%20San%20Francisco%20and%20%26quot%3BGo%20back%20to%20being%20the%20king.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWell%2C%20here.%20So%2C%20first%20let's%20just%20be%20clear%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Kalanick.%20%26quot%3BOn%20December%2018th%2C%20I%20moved%20to%20Texas.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20I'm%20a%20primary%20resident%20of%20Texas%2C%26quot%3B%20Kalanick%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKalanick%20was%20born%20and%20raised%20in%20the%20Los%20Angeles%20area.%20He%20attended%20UCLA%20and%20maintained%20residences%20in%20Los%20Angeles.%20He%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuber-ceo-travis-kalanick-life-rise-and-fall-photos-resigned-2017-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eco-founded%20Uber%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20San%20Francisco%20and%20resigned%20as%20its%20CEO%20in%202017%20after%20facing%20investor%20pressure%20stemming%20from%20reports%20of%20a%20toxic%20work%20culture%20and%20multiple%20clashes%20with%20regulators.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKalanick%20did%20not%20detail%20the%20reasons%20he%20moved%20to%20Texas%2C%20but%20he%20joins%20a%20growing%20list%20of%20billionaires%20who%20built%20their%20careers%20in%20California%20but%20left%20the%20state%2C%20either%20as%20individuals%20or%20as%20businesses%2C%20since%20COVID.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20have%20flocked%20to%20Florida%2C%20while%20others%20have%20moved%20to%20Texas%2C%20citing%20favorable%20tax%20policies%20and%20business%20regulations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElon%20Musk%2C%20the%20Tesla%20CEO%2C%20founded%20SpaceX%20in%20California%20but%20relocated%20to%20Texas%20in%202020.%20While%20Tesla%20and%20SpaceX%20have%20a%20large%20presence%20in%20California%2C%20Tesla's%20headquarters%20are%20in%20Austin%2C%20and%20in%202024%2C%20Musk%20said%20SpaceX%20would%20move%20its%20HQ%20to%20Starship%2C%20Texas.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20Oracle%20similarly%20announced%20that%20it%20had%20moved%20its%20headquarters%20from%20Silicon%20Valley%20to%20Austin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%20of%20the%20tech%20boom%20in%20Texas%2C%20billions%20are%20pouring%20into%20the%20state%2C%20mostly%20for%20company%20expansion%20and%20the%20race%20to%20build%20data%20centers.%20Austin%20in%20particular%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20major%20destination%20for%20technology%20companies%20and%20investors%2C%20often%20dubbed%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faustin-texas-silicon-hills-tech-capital-city-photos-2019-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESilicon%20Hills%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%20Google%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20announced%20a%20%2440%20billion%20investment%20plan%20through%202027%20to%20expand%20data%20centers%2C%20cloud%20capabilities%2C%20and%20new%20campuses%20in%20Texas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECalifornia%20has%20floated%20a%20one-time%20billionaire%20wealth%20tax%20to%20support%20the%20state's%20funding%20for%20schools%20and%20heal