iscipline%20and%20resourcefulness.%20With%20no%20access%20to%20coaching%20centres%2C%20she%20built%20her%20own%20roadmap%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F404958%2Firs-officer-shares-strategy-role-ncert-book-upsc-preparation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENCERTs%20for%20basics%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20Geography%2C%20History%2C%20and%20Economics.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EM.%20Laxmikanth%20for%20Polity.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOnline%20research%20and%20YouTube%20lectures%20for%20Jharkhand-specific%20topics%2C%20since%20most%20standard%20books%20weren%E2%80%99t%20available%20in%20English.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPrevious%20Year%20Questions%20(PYQs)%20as%20her%20strongest%20tool.%20%E2%80%9CA%20lot%20of%20JPSC%20questions%20repeat%20in%20some%20form.%20So%2C%20PYQs%20were%20a%20blessing%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20mantra%20was%20simple%3A%20read%20less%2C%20revise%20more.%20She%20made%20detailed%20notes%2C%20revised%20them%20multiple%20times%2C%20and%20stuck%20to%20one%20source%20instead%20of%20chasing%20dozens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMany%20believe%20that%20coaching%20is%20necessary%2C%20but%20I%20want%20to%20tell%20every%20aspirant%2C%20it%20is%20not%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rupam%20stresses.%20%E2%80%9CConsistency%2C%20patience%2C%20and%20determination%20are%20far%20more%20important%20than%20expensive%20coaching%20classes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20result%20day%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20July%20at%203%3A30%20am%2C%20Rupam%20received%20a%20call%20from%20a%20Deputy%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20who%20had%20taken%20her%20mock%20interview.%20The%20words%20on%20the%20other%20end%20left%20her%20stunned%3A%20%E2%80%9CRupam%2C%20you%20have%20cleared%20JPSC.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStill%20half-asleep%2C%20she%20was%20first%20shocked%2C%20then%20overwhelmed.%