%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enative%20trees%20conserve%20water%2C%20regenerate%20soil%20health%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20support%20biodiversity.%20Vishal%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CTrees%20improve%20soil%20moisture%2C%20reduce%20evaporation%2C%20and%20create%20micro-channels%20that%20hold%20rainwater.%20An%20acre%20of%20forest%20can%20save%20over%2012%20million%20litres%20of%20water%20annually%20compared%20to%20conventional%20paddy%20fields.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGurpreet%20reinforces%20the%20connection%3A%20%E2%80%9CWater%20and%20trees%20are%20intertwined.%20By%20protecting%20one%2C%20we%20safeguard%20the%20other.%20Punjab%E2%80%99s%20future%20depends%20on%20this%20balance.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWho%20owns%20a%20mini%20forest%3F%20The%20power%20of%20local%20pride%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20balance%20is%20being%20rebuilt%20not%20through%20imposition%20but%20collaboration.%20Much%20of%20the%20land%20is%20government-owned%2C%20but%20when%20individuals%20like%20Inderjit%20offer%20private%20land%2C%20it%20fosters%20co-ownership%20and%20responsibility.%20%E2%80%9CVillages%20take%20ownership%2C%20and%20that%20is%20why%20survival%20rates%20of%20trees%20are%20so%20high%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vishal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20many%20places%2C%20schools%20are%20involved%2C%20turning%20forests%20into%20living%20classrooms%20where%20children%20learn%20about%20ecology%20and%20conservation.%20%E2%80%9CChildren%20see%20the%20trees%20grow%20and%20learn%20to%20respect%20nature%2C%E2%80%9D%20Inderjit%20smiles.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20plants%20seeds%20of%20awareness%20that%20will%20last%20generations.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20planting%20a%20few%20saplings%20in%20one%20village%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Billion%20Tree%20Project%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20grown%20into%20a%20statewide%20movement%20spanning%2017%20districts.%20Each%20of%20the%20three%20million%20trees%20has%20been%20carefully%20tracked%2C%20with%20survival%20rates%20monitored%20through%20rigorous%20documentation%20and%20local%20engagement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-08-14-at-13.10.25_87c06412-2_11zon-1756996907-500x375.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20native%20trees%20help%20to%20use%20water%20wisely%20and%20improve%20the%20health%20of%20the%20soil%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-08-14-at-13.10.25_87c06412-2_11zon-1756996907-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-08-14-at-13.10.25_87c06412-2_11zon-1756996907-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-08-14-at-13.10.25_87c06412-2_11zon-1756996907-768x576.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-08-14-at-13.10.25_87c06412-2_11zon-1756996907-1200x900.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-08-14-at-13.10.25_87c06412-2_11zon-1756996907-800x600.jpg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-08-14-at-13.10.25_87c06412-2_11zon-1756996907-600x450.jpg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-08-14-at-13.10.25_87c06412-2_11zon-1756996907-400x300.jpg%20400w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-08-14-at-13.10.25_87c06412-2_11zon-1756996907-200x150.jpg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-08-14-at-13.10.25_87c06412-2_11zon-1756996907-150x113.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-08-14-at-13.10.25_87c06412-2_11zon-1756996907.jpg%201280w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-496574%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22375%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20native%20trees%20help%20to%20use%20water%20wisely%20and%20improve%20the%20health%20of%20the%20soil%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20don%E2%80%99t%20just%20plant%20and%20walk%20away%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vishal.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20map%20each%20site%20using%20KML%20Polygons%20%E2%80%94%20satellite-based%20tools%20that%20log%20the%20exact%20coordinates%20of%20every%20mini%20forest.%20This%20lets%20us%20maintain%20a%20digital%20record%2C%20verify%20locations%2C%20and%20track%20growth.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20forests%20are%20feeding%20families%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20project%E2%80%99s%20social%20impact%20matches%20its%20ecological%20gains.%20Beyond%20trees%2C%20it%20has%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F418054%2Fneeti-goel-restaurateur-mumbai-khaanachiye-lb-trust-sundarbans-tiger-widows%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebecome%20a%20source%20of%20livelihood%20for%20thousands%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20rural%20Punjab.%20Around%20120%20people%20work%20at%20its%20nurseries%2C%20and%20the%20initiative%20collaborates%20with%20the%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20National%20Rural%20Employment%20Guarantee%20Act%20(MGNREGA)%20to%20scale%20up%20plantations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20end%20of%202024%2C%20TBTP%20had%20generated%20more%20than%2015%2C000%20jobs%20through%20MGNREGA%2C%20most%20filled%20by%20women%20and%20young%20people.%20These%20roles%20extend%20beyond%20wages%2C%20involving%20environmental%20custodianship%20from%20land%20preparation%20to%20sapling%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMGNREGA%20has%20been%20instrumental%20in%20bringing%20in%20local%20workers%20who%20not%20only%20earn%20but%20also%20develop%20a%20sense%20of%20responsibility%20towards%20the%20land.%20When%20someone%20helps%20raise%20a%20forest%20from%20scratch%2C%20it%20becomes%20personal%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vishal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20watched%20young%20people%20grow%20into%20community%20leaders%20through%20this%20work.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20educate%20their%20neighbours%2C%20advocate%20for%20conservation%2C%20and%20carry%20the%20torch%20forward%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20sun%20sets%20over%20Rajinder%20Nagar%2C%20Inderjit%20walks%20slowly%20through%20his%20forest.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20the%20Punjab%20I%20remember%20as%20a%20child%20%E2%80%94%20lush%2C%20vibrant%2C%20alive.%20It%20is%20coming%20back%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20In%20Lang%2C%20Romanpreet%20watches%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F493007%2Fbutterfly-friendly-plants-for-indian-homes-marigold-hibiscus-tulsi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebutterflies%20flit%20through%20the%20branches%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T201626.909_11zon-1756997217.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Billion%20Tree%20Project%20helps%20to%20plant%20trees%20and%20is%20a%20consistent%20source%20of%20livelihood%20for%20many%20villagers%2C%20especially%20women%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T201626.909_11zon-1756997217.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T201626.909_11zon-1756997217-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T201626.909_11zon-1756997217-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T201626.909_11zon-1756997217-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T201626.909_11zon-1756997217-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-496582%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Billion%20Tree%20Project%20helps%20to%20plant%20trees%20and%20is%20a%20consistent%20source%20of%20livelihood%20for%20many%20villagers%2C%20especially%20women%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Billion%20Tree%20Project%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20not%20only%20about%20greening%20land%20but%20about%20rekindling%20identity%2C%20reviving%20community%2C%20and%20reimagining%20a%20future%20in%20harmony%20with%20nature.%20Gurpreet%20puts%20it%20aptly%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPlanting%20a%20tree%20is%20an%20act%20of%20faith%20in%20the%20future.%20It%20is%20a%20promise%20that%20we%20care%2C%20that%20we%20will%20nurture%2C%20and%20that%20we%20believe%20in%20the%20resilience%20of%20this%20land%20and%20its%20people.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAll%20pictures%20courtesy%20Roundglass%20Foundation%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1757215800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T195457.273_11zon-1756995925.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D496504%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Roundglass%20Foundation%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98The%20Billion%20Tree%20Project%E2%80%99%20has%20planted%20over%203%20million%20native%20trees%20across%20Punjab