on%20and%20sustainability%20can%20go%20hand%20in%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECouples%20can%20frame%20them%2C%20pass%20them%20down%2C%20or%20simply%20keep%20them%20folded%20away%2C%20soft%20with%20yarn%20and%20memory.%20In%20a%20wedding%20culture%20obsessed%20with%20grandeur%2C%20crochet%20%3Cem%3Evarmalas%20%3C%2Fem%3Eremind%20us%20of%20something%20simpler%20yet%20profound.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELove%2C%20after%20all%2C%20is%20meant%20to%20last.%20Why%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20the%20garlands%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1757129400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-09-04T014422.986-1756930470.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D496018%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Once%20seen%20only%20in%20sweaters%20and%20cushion%20covers%2C%20crochet%20has%20now%20entered%20Indian%20weddings%20through%20crochet%20%E2%80%98varmalas%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20garlands%20that%20don%E2%80%99t%20wilt%2C%20but%20last%20forever.%20Couples%20are%20embracing%20them%20as%20sustainable%2C%20sentimental%20keepsakes%20that%20turn%20a%20traditional%20ritual%20into%20timeless%20art.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Srimoyee%20Chowdhury%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F496018%2Fcrochet-varmalas-indian-weddings-sustainable-ananya-malhotra-manya-jain-trending-garlands%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22As%20Floods%20Ravage%20Punjab%2C%203.5%20Lakh%20Struggle%20To%20Survive.%20Be%20Their%20Lifeline%2C%20Donate%20Today%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFarmer%20Mohan%20Singh%20was%20preparing%20to%20harvest%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekharif%20%3C%2Fem%3Ecrops%20on%20his%20field%20this%20week.%20He%20was%20elated%3B%20it%20had%20been%20a%20great%20season.%20So%20picture%20his%20devastation%20when%20he%20walked%20out%20onto%20his%20field%20three%20days%20ago%2C%20and%20saw%20that%20the%20green%20had%20been%20replaced%20by%20